author: kelvingoodson
msg: TUSCANY-1393 Ron's fix ensures the correct type of primitive is used to store primitive values in the EMF NotificationImpl.  Without this fix, attempts to serialize a change summary fail with a class cast exception because,e.g. the changed int primitive has been stored in a double, and the attempt to cast it back into an int fails.
